{"about_the_game":"A Case of Distrust is a narrative mystery from 1924 San Francisco. Play as private investigator Phyllis Cadence Malone in this historical 2D adventure game. Explore underground speakeasies, smoke-filled billiard halls, classic barber shops, and more. Catch suspects in lies by using evidence, statements, and your wits. Intrinsic challenges face our heroine, as she struggles against a pushback on emancipation, leading to many doubts, both internal and external. Uncover the truth in a mystery full of deception!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A hardboiled mystery, working past deceptive characters towards the truth<br></li><li>1924 San Francisco with historically accurate details<br></li><li>Saul Bass inspired visuals and scene transitions<br></li><li>Finger-snapping music that gives style to the roaring 20s<br></li><li>Themes of poverty, racism, and emancipation that tie into contemporary issues</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"No Food Here","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/717610/d690dc9cd1a3d7945cc36f8399e435a4373d4580.jpg"},{"name":"On the Job","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/717610/b35e26f24d3870c75cfec85e98b7c1ccfe7a2b83.jpg"},{"name":"Vision","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/717610/35c28a9e8490f5e1e8d9a383ba37d44592270a1c.jpg"},{"name":"Master Sleuth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/717610/8df9fa52f270475ee320275b59ce8eea08f9a068.jpg"},{"name":"My Zaide","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/717610/6c14abf217f54d9fb6026e71efb0ca86da67a256.jpg"},{"name":"Becoming Learned","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/717610/80275efb1de4f9faf352843477d0bc87439f27b3.jpg"},{"name":"The Capital","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/ima